data.description: UPDATED 5 bedroom 2.5 bath home with just over 3,000 square feet on a LARGE LOT in desirable Salem Woods. House BACKS TO TREES that gives house a PRIVATE VIEW.  Inside there is an OPEN KITCHEN with 3 PANTRIES & a BREAKFAST NOOK & SS appliances. Also, house has 2 STAIRCASES that lead upstairs, LVP FLOORS downstairs, TILE foyer, NEWER CARPET upstairs and newer light fixtures. DUAL ZONED HVAC with outside units. MOVE IN READY!  Don't wait too long to see this one!!
